text: Pine Tavern is an unincorporated community located along the border of Elk Township in Gloucester County and Upper Pittsgrove, Salem County, New Jersey, United States. Once known as Pineville, the community had a store, tavern, and post office. ==References== Category:Elk Township, New Jersey Category:Unincorporated communities in Salem County, New Jersey Category:Unincorporated communities in New Jersey
title: Pine Tavern, New Jersey
